Ok...I promised an update so here it is...

The weekend started out awesome  and then about 2 sessions in we started experiencing a bit of rain...It was on and off most of the day, but we still went crash free all… https://t.co/iXptyjJ6in

What an awesome 1st day...even with a little rain we still went incident free and graduated 5 new students into the sanctioned Roadracing community!!!

Belladonna Britanni
Nicole Marie Ball
Marcella Alejandra… https://t.co/g9R4FoMq40
